notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the kernel SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 9.4. It addresses 21 CVEs: CVE-2023-53401, CVE-2022-50367, CVE-2025-39730, CVE-2023-53331, CVE-2025-39718, and 16 more.
